highlights.text: “Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 168 days straight.
Kendrick Lamar has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “luther (with sza)” is the highest at #12.
“peekaboo (feat. azchike)” by Kendrick Lamar and AZ Chike is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #98.
“PSA” by SZA is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 8 spots at #91.
